## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources, which may not cover all cultural perspectives or academic insights. The reliance on user-generated content, such as Quora, may introduce subjective biases. Additionally, the dynamic and complex nature of culture and identity means that interpretations can vary widely across different contexts and disciplines. Further research, including empirical studies, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic.